  "text": "All different statistical analyses are also described in details in [CITATION_1] . Responses were first analysed to remove error trials (RTs less than 100 ms and RTs greater than 1000 ms). Percentage of false alarms and percentage of misses were analyzed by one-way nonparametric repeated measures analyses of variance (ANOVA; the Friedman test). p,.05 was considered to be statistically significant.",
